<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10055] Add option to limit the scan speed in CopyTable and VerifyReplication</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10055</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add option to limit the scan speed in CopyTable and VerifyReplication.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When adding a new replication, we use &apos;CopyTable&apos; to copy old data from online cluster to peer cluster.  After that, we use &apos;VerifyReplication&apos; to check the data consistency of two clusters.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To reduce the impact the online cluster&apos;s service, we add an option to limit the scan speed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>
</environment>
